name: Flying Plane Cruise Ship Parking Simulation
name_original: Flying Plane Cruise Ship Parking Simulation
description:
This time you are the pilot of an jet fighter, and parking a jet fighter is something totally different then parking a truck, bus or car.
In flying plane cruise ship parking simulation game ,you learn to park your jet fighter on the navy's aircraft carrier!
This is a realistic parking simulation involving planes, helicopters and more! The pilot needs to park the planes into the right place.
